data.description: Welcome to a charming ranch-style home in a quiet, sought-after neighborhood. Enjoy the spaciousness of a full walkout basement and a large fenced yard. The main level features 3 bedrooms, a full bath, kitchen, dining room and living room with a beautiful brick fireplace. Step onto the balcony from the living room, and enjoy a cup of coffee in your peaceful backyard. Downstairs offers a bedroom, a great room with another brick fireplace, a full bath, storage, and a laundry room. With a 2-car attached garage, this property combines comfort and convenience for a perfect home in a cozy setting!
